<br>
Equipping... you could do some of the Lodi Kai quests in Shadeweavers or whack lots and lots of the worms and hoppers for silks and hides.  The Shak Dratha have shade silk and you can make that into shade silk robes which (while not incredible armor) are wearable by all/all so can be handy for rogues and bards and others wanting a robe but not able to wear one.  <br>
<br>
To get money.. yeah wisps and then the book quest.  Or you can whack Ogres in Butcherblock  for an occassional medallion.  Bone chips are needed for a lot of faction quests so you might be able to sell them to players.  <br>
